Pillow
======

Python Imaging Library (Fork)
-----------------------------

Pillow is the friendly PIL fork by [Alex Clark and Contributors]_. PIL is
the Python Imaging Library by Fredrik Lundh and Contributors. As of 2019,
Pillow development is [supported by Tidelift]_.

